If you want to modify the relative path before injecting your file into HDFS, you can modify the header [`CamelFileName`][1] (that you can get from the constant `HdfsConstants.FILE_NAME`) to fit your requirements.

So in your case, your `Processor` could rather be something like:

```
public class FileProcessor implements Processor {

    @Override
    public void process(Exchange exchange) {
        exchange.getIn().setHeader(
            HdfsConstants.FILE_NAME,
            exchange.getIn().getHeader(HdfsConstants.FILE_NAME, String.class)
                .replace(&#39;\\&#39;, &#39;/&#39;)
        );
    }
}
```


  [1]: https://camel.apache.org/components/3.18.x/hdfs-component.html#_endpoint_header_CamelFileName

